name: Weird Future Fashion [LoRA]
description:
UPDATE:

v5: New training method

Full changelog below

This lora has been trained with images of weird fashion trends and random futuristic artists renditions of clothing that will never make the shelves. Apply this to any v1.5 SD model.

Use the prompt 'weird future fashion' in combination the other optional trigger words. At weight 1 it does get pretty opinionated about clothing and styles. Go beyond 1 to get TRULY weird!

Testing and sample images generated using the following models:

  • Deliberate v2

  • ICBINP

  • Babes 2.0

  • Custom checkpoint (similar to Comic Babes v1)

If you like this, check out my other models!

Full Changelog

  • v4: More images in training, more colorful, generally more functional

  • v3: Better LoRA training, smaller filesize, more stable (heh) and much better at handling prompts

  • v2: Expanded dataset, better handling non cloths related prompts

  • v1: Initial model
